\c 72
\s Ukuru hwaMambo Pisarema raSoromoni.
\p
\v 1 Ipai mambo zvamakatonga, Mwari,
\s Nokururama kwenyu kumwanakomana wamambo.
\p
\v 2 Achatongera vanhu venyu nokururama,
\s Navarombo venyu achavaruramisira.
\p
\v 3 Makomo nezvikomo achavigira vanhu rugare,
\s Yl√≤hrurama.
\p
\v 4 Achatongera varombo vavanhu, Achaponesa vana vavashaiwi, Nokupwanya mumanikidzi.
\p
\v 5 Vachakutyai kana zuva richipo, Uye kana mwedzi uchipo, kusvikira kumarudzi namarudzi.
\p
\v 6 Achaburuka iye semvura pauswa hwakagurirwa;
\s Semvura inonaya ichidiridza pasi.
\p
\v 7 Nemisi yake akarurama achakura zvakanaka;
\s Rugare rwakawanda ruchavapo,
\s kusvikira mwedzi waguma.
\p
\v 8 Achabata ushe kubva pagungwa kusvikira pagungwa,
\s Nokubva paRwizi kusvikira kumigumo yapasi.
\p
\v 9 Vagere parnarenje vachapfugama pamberi pake;
\s Vavengi vake vachananzva guruva.
\p
\v 10 Madzimambo eTarishishi neezvivi achauya nezvipo;
\s Madzimambo eShebha neSebha vachamuvigira zvipo;
\p
\v 11 Zvirokwazvo, madzimambo ose achawira
\s pasi pamberi pake;
\s Ndudzi dzose dzichamushumira.
\p
\v 12 Nokuti acharwira mushaiwi kana achidanidzira;
\s Nomurombo asina mubatsiri.
\p
\v 13 Achanzwira nyasha murombo nomushaiwi,
\s Achaponesa mweya yavashaiwi.
\p
\v 14 Achadzikinura mweya yavo pakutambudzika napakumanikidzwa;
\s Ropa ravo richava chinhu chinokosha pamberi pake;
\p
\v 15 Iye achararama, achapiwa ndarama yeShebha;
\s Vanhu vacharamba vachimunyengeterera; Vachamuvonga zuva rose.
\p
\v 16 Kuchava nezviyo zvizhinji pasi pamusoro pamakomo;
\s Zvibereko zvazvo zvichavhunga seRebhanoni;
\s Vanogara paguta vachakura souswa pasi.
\p
\v 17 Zita rake richavapo nokusingaperi; Zita rake richagara riripo panguva yose yokuvapo kwezuva;
\s Vanhu vacharopafadzwa maari; Ndudzi dzose dzichati, "Anomufaro."
\p
\v 18 Jehovha Mwari, iye Mwari waIsiraeri, ngaarumbidzwe, Iye oga anoita zvinoshamisa.
\p
\v 19 Zita rake rinobwinya
\s ngarirumbidzwe nokusingaperi; Pasi pose ngapazadzwe
\s nokubwinya kwenyu. Ameni, Ameni.
\p
\v 20 Minyengetero yaDhavhidhi mwanakomana waJese yapera.
